headline.main: Mexico Police Rescue 31 Cuban Migrants in Cancun
headline.print_headline: Mexico Police Rescue 31 Cuban Migrants in Cancun

lead_paragraph: Mexican federal police rescued 31 Cuban immigrants who had been held in a house in the resort city of Cancun, the government said on Saturday.
